---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro"
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Team from "../components/Team.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <main class="space-y-20">
        <Container>
            <div class="relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center md:flex-row" id="hero">
                <div class="row items-center py-5 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
                    <div class="text-center space-y-10">
                        <h2 class="text-5xl font-medium leading-none md:text-6xl">Privacy Policy</h2>
                        <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">
                            At Data Forge Technologies, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, 
                            use, and share your information when you use our services, including our interaction 
                            through the WhatsApp API.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Information We Collect</h3>
                <p><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We may collect your name, phone number, email, and address when you register for our services or communicate with us.</p>
                <p><strong>Usage Information:</strong> We collect data on how you interact with our services, including WhatsApp.</p>
                <p><strong>Technical Information:</strong> We collect data such as IP address, device type, and cookies.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                <p><strong>Service Provision:</strong> We use your information to improve our services, including managing inquiries and appointments.</p>
                <p><strong>Communication:</strong> We use WhatsApp to respond to inquiries and notify you about appointments and promotions.</p>
                <p><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> We may use your information to comply with legal obligations and protect our rights.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Information Sharing</h3>
                <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except when necessary to provide our services or as required by law.</p>
                <p>We may share information with service providers such as hosting and messaging platforms.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Information Security</h3>
                <p>We implement security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Your Rights</h3>
                <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Changes to This Policy</h3>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Contact</h3>
                <p>If you have any questions, you can contact us at <strong>dataforge.tch@gmail.com</strong> or <strong>+57(321)741-9283</strong>.</p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </main>
</Layout>
